SAML Authorisation Service
==========================
This directory contains the configuration information for an authorisation 
test service used by the unit tests:

 - authorisation-service.ini: main configuration file for the service 
   
 - authorisationserviceapp.py: script to invoke the service:
 
   $ python ./authorisationserviceapp.py
   
   This script can be used to test the service but the unit tests start up and
   close down attribute authority instances automatically.  See: 
   ndg.security.test.unit.BaseTestCase
      
 - Testing - using ndg_saml_client CLI tool from ndg_saml package:
 
   $ ndg_saml_client authz -u https://localhost:9443/authorisation-service \
      -s https://localhost:7443/openid/philip.kershaw -S urn:esg:openid \
      -C ../pki/ca -r http://localhost/test_accessGrantedToSecuredURI -p